displayctl (1.0.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release.
  * Multi-monitor display mode control (mirror, extend, second, PC)
  * X11 (xrandr) and Wayland (wlr-randr) backend support
  * Profile save/load with EDID fingerprinting
  * Hotplug daemon with udev integration
  * Systemd user service for auto-start

 -- Displayctl Maintainer <maintainer@displayctl.dev>  Sun, 21 Jun 2026 00:00:00 +0000
